dct_title_s: Exactissima et postomnes alias nunc demùm edita tabula continens perfectam descriptionem regnorum Arragoniæ et Navarræ, principatûs Cataloniæ : nec non partium conterminarum, Biscajæ utriusque Castellæ, ac Valentiæ
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. The Ottens family firm continued under brothers Reinier and Josua after the death of their mother in 1725, until the death of Reinier in 1750. cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers.
dct_publisher_sm: Amst. Batavo [Amsterdam : R. and J. Ottens, between 1725 and 1750]
